{"tid":1061980,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"垃圾炒麵王難食咗好多","createTime":"2019-03-14T19:33:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T14:20:10.000Z","uid":175663,"like":11,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b7d873d59801775183e7ee44195bd2ce2ba50ca7","tid":1061980,"uid":175663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T19:33:28.000Z","msg":"話說小弟冇食炒麵王好多年，印象中幾好食嘅。前排係7仔見到，就買返屋企回味下啦。屌你老母炒麵王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，食咗2啖已經食唔到落去。蠔油味，避風堂味都一樣咁垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，啲味好怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係屌你老母哂錢拎去比狗食算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad900becb1787ed06b4d4be70e8dee2e9e01316f","tid":1061980,"uid":124491,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T19:35:16.000Z","msg":"回憶永遠是美好的 btw 紅色先好食"},{"pid":"09d33a01e92b5e1910d42c836a786f20673f9f19","tid":1061980,"uid":3167,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T19:54:46.000Z","msg":"前排759有日本個炒麵10蚊<br />\n轉左包裝炒麵王垃圾"},{"pid":"b9d0bf8e3d032d2e35217a84b569b3382b12c8bf","tid":1061980,"uid":227275,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T16:56:20.000Z","msg":"不嬲垃圾 得個平<br />\n好餓果時做宵夜就還可以<br />\n如果營多可以咁方便就煮到就好"},{"pid":"7a405bd11c0a9358c6117ec2341d31fbdc6b3af5","tid":1061980,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T17:33:29.000Z","msg":"好撚咸，重味精"},{"pid":"84d855ccfde7a6182bc753e0c657c1f8f35e48a5","tid":1061980,"uid":27416,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T17:36:41.000Z","msg":"唔係佢難食左<br />\n係你要求高左"},{"pid":"76d6c11d0094a3f61328ebdeb4d98c9a9f194889","tid":1061980,"uid":76375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T01:09:54.000Z","msg":"算變得比較少了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且紅色難食左 藍色好食左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hk